    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J74">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A Lady red -- amid the Hill</l>
                    <l>Her annual secret keeps!</l>
                    <l>A Lady white, within the Field</l>
                    <l>In Placid Lily sleeps!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The tidy Breezes, with their Brooms --</l>
                    <l>Sweep vale -- and hill -- and tree!</l>
                    <l>Prithee, My pretty Housewives!</l>
                    <l>Who may expected be?</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Neighbors do not yet suspect!</l>
                    <l>The Woods exchange a smile!</l>
                    <l>Orchard, and Buttercup, and Bird</l>
                    <l>In such a little while!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And yet, how still the Landscape stands!</l>
                    <l>How nonchalant the Hedge!</l>
                    <l>As if the "Resurrection"</l>
                    <l>Were nothing very strange!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
